IMPORT ./rules.hmn
IMPORT ./flows.hmn

AGENT support_bot
SYSTEM ./system.md

CONSTRAINTS response
  MUST respond within 2 sentences for simple questions
  NEVER leave the customer waiting without acknowledgment
  SHOULD end with a clear next step

FLOW close
  ask if there is anything else
  thank the customer
  end the conversation

TEST
  INPUT "I need help with my bill"
  EXPECT CONTAINS "billing"
  INPUT "Where is my package?"
  EXPECT NOT CONTAINS "error"
